{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were never seen by their families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In some cases at the very beginning, some of them were able to smuggle out-- the restrictions weren't so tight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how did they get these people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They get these people-- they had-- they-- they actually grabbed them on the street or else there were lists and they were notified so and so has to report to such and such.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then if you didn't report, they came after you and they made you report.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naturally, we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father and my brother and myself, we were working in this factory, which was another street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This factory was a known big factory, shoe factory, owned by the people, ironically, in the same name of our own but there was no relationship.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We worked there from 1940, '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after work, we came home, eight o'clock you had to be in the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anybody being caught with a radio was shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this happened every day, so naturally we were very frightened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'll tell you this much, we heard people being shot in the street at eight o'clock who came in late.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One time I had an incident, how I escaped was just God was with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came home five minutes late, I was too energetic and too active to submit myself to these restrictions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However painful they were, you try to be a wise guy sometimes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In this particular case, I came home about five minutes after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I came home, I ran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw the streets are clean and my-- my heart was pounding and I knew I was late.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I may not have known how late I was, but I was pretty close to eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the streets are empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
